      <div class="ep-framework-card">
        <h4 id="eligibility">Retirement Eligibility</h4>
        <p>Multiple pathways to retirement with different requirements and benefits. Know your MRA, understand immediate versus deferred retirement, and optimize your timing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ep-framework-card">
        <h4 id="supplement">FERS Supplement</h4>
        <p>Bridge benefit from retirement until Social Security eligibility at 62. Understand who qualifies, earnings test limits, and coordination strategies.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ep-framework-card">
        <h4>Survivor Benefits</h4>
        <p>Critical irrevocable decision on spouse protection. Compare full survivor benefit, partial benefits, and no election to optimize lifetime income.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

